# Title: Decode Base64 Encoded Text
# Author: Daniil Yugoslavskiy, oscd.community
# Date: 2020-10-19
# Level: low
# Description: Detects usage of base64 utility to decode arbitrary base64-encoded text
# MITRE Tactic: Defense Evasion
# Tags: attack.defense-evasion, attack.t1027
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/linux/process_creation/proc_creation_lnx_base64_decode.yml
# False Positives:
#   - Legitimate activities

CommandLine="*-d*" Image="*/base64"